metadata.name: Found Abe Mint Pass
metadata.description: The Found Abe Collection consists of Found Abe Mint Passes that can be acquired only two ways; Finding a real US five dollar bill with a FOUNDABE.COM stamp or purchasing one off of a secondary market like OpenSea or LooksRare. The mint pass allows the holder to mint a Descendents of Abe NFT for FREE, plus guarantees the holder a 48 hour window to mint a Descendents of Abe NFT before the mint is open to the public.
